race.comment: Competitive. GRINZINGER LASS (3) recorded a determined win last start by 0.9 lengths over 1200m, going back-to-back. She improved again and jumps from the inside gate. Will get every chance to deliver the hat-trick. BOY BIG (1) was an emphatic winner last time over 1000m. Has a strong record this journey and will take beating again. THE GIRL'S BOY (2) was a winner over 1300m at Darwin last time out, coming home with a powerful run to score comfortably. Rolls up on a 9-day return but has to come back 200m, and that's the niggle. TANGO STEPZ (4) was back on track placing over 1200m. Tumbles in weight today and that brings her into it. BOLD TROPIC (5) won't be far away off an improved run.
